{"tid":192056,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"港大校訓：明德格物","createTime":"2017-04-08T10:27:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T03:45:59.000Z","uid":10171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b49d5224fc1bfa78a1de2973e9e5451f3cbc033e","tid":192056,"uid":10171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T10:27:04.000Z","msg":"「明明德」 &mdash; 第一個「明」字是使動詞，第二個「明」字是形容詞。<span style=\"color: red;\">「明德」是人與生俱來的光明皎潔的德性。「明明德」就是讓這種德性彰顯出來，並將它發揚光大，然後推己及人，使天下的人都能夠彰明其明德，同歸於至善。</span>校訓將「明明德」簡稱為「明德」。<br />\n <br />\n「格物」是八條目的根本，也就是「明明德」的基本工夫。<span style=\"color: red;\">「格物」指窮究事物的原理，而「格物」最基本的方法就是讀書。</span>「格物」的目的在於「致知」，即擁有淵博的知識。從「格物」、「致知」順推，即一步步做下去，才能達到「明明德於天下」的終極目的。「明明德於天下」，則天下太平。<br />\n<br />\nHall culture完全實踐到明德格物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7821a1c3ddc66b722eeb9615c12015c3aae82c","tid":192056,"uid":29645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T10:27:59.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9d8bc655387f0e591147af0f4c148dc697f2e8","tid":192056,"uid":74827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T10:29:25.000Z","msg":"果然係kongu文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4122e2577e1170b43bf3cd774df0b7f9c373c5d0","tid":192056,"uid":10171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T10:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c15b7fe24717b092262563eea88c7d3bfe9ef0","tid":192056,"uid":99828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T10:41:15.000Z","msg":"推已及人？推啲人去死咋掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b945ee98743cf533dbd51bf0d95dd153e23de0a","tid":192056,"uid":10171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T11:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset